data.description: Fantastic location! Welcome to this beautiful  home located in Fort Mill; Award-winning schools, Anne Springs Close Greenway, downtown Fort Mill w/ fantastic restaurants & breweries nearby. This beautiful home is as impressive as it is functional. Bright & airy plan w/ formal dining, large eat in kitchen. Speaker System, irrigation system, widened Driveway ,A NEW ROOF(2023) and brand NEW HVAC (2023)! There is plenty of space in this home w/ 5 BEDS, 4 FULL BATHS, 2nd floor LOFT, & ADDITIONAL THIRD FLOOR BONUS ROOM perfect for large families or to comfortably entertain. Main level features an open concept with intricate details such as crown moldings, hardwood floors, gourmet kitchen w/HUGE center island, office space, & guest bed & full bath. The 2nd floor has the cozy loft, master suite and spa-like bath along with 3 other bedrooms & 2 bathrooms (one is a Jack & Jill)! 3rd floor bonus space could be perfect for a 6th bedroom a home theater or a man cave!
